import React, {useState, useContext} from "react";
import {FormGroup, Label, Input, FormText} from "reactstrap";
import {AvForm, AvField, AvInput} from "availity-reactstrap-validation";

const AddUser = () => {
	return (
		<React.Fragment>
			<AvForm className="needs-validation mt-3">
				<Row>
					<Col md="6"></Col>
				</Row>
				<FormGroup>
					<Label for="fullname">Nombre</Label>
					<Input type="text" name="name" id="name" />
				</FormGroup>
				<FormGroup>
					<Label for="fullname">Apellido</Label>
					<Input type="text" name="surname" id="surname" />
				</FormGroup>
				<FormGroup>
					<Label for="age">Edad</Label>
					<Input type="text" name="age" id="age" />
				</FormGroup>
				<Label for="gender">Sexo</Label>
				<FormGroup check>
					<Label check>
						<Input type="radio" name="gender" defaultChecked /> Masculino
					</Label>
				</FormGroup>
				<FormGroup check>
					<Label check>
						<Input type="radio" name="gender" /> Femenino
					</Label>
				</FormGroup>
				<FormGroup>
					<Label for="exampleSelect">Nivel de confianza</Label>
					<Input type="select" name="select" id="exampleSelect">
						<option>1</option>
						<option>2</option>
						<option>3</option>
						<option>4</option>
						<option>5</option>
					</Input>
				</FormGroup>
				<FormGroup className="mt-3">
					<FormGroup>
						<Label for="exampleFile">Foto del rostro</Label>
						<Input type="file" name="file" id="exampleFile" className="" />
						<FormText color="muted">Formatos permitidos: .jpg y .png</FormText>
					</FormGroup>
				</FormGroup>
			</AvForm>
		</React.Fragment>
	);
};

export default AddUser;
